    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty in person. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014not a single scratch or blemish to be found, and the interior still has that fresh, new car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and has been super reliable. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 45500.0,
