    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, showcasing an impeccable F22C1 inline-four power plant with factory-spec compression across all cylinders. This front-midship chassis retains all original VIN tags on body panels and features a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation. The close-ratio six-speed manual transmission provides crisp, notch-free engagement, paired with a flawlessly functioning Torsen limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true to factory alignment, utilizing the original double-wishbone setup with no bushing degradation. This is a collector-tier example with a documented service history, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
