    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle is in breathtaking condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free of any creasing or wear, and still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every technological feature and electronic component operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage reflects the vehicle's low-mileage, fair-weather-only history. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved example of automotive excellence. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title.",
