      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single mark on it. It drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Come see it for yourself!",
